    "Notes: On 10,000 Congressional bills, we prompt GPT-3.5-Turbo and GPT-4o to label each description for its policy topic area using alternative prompting strategies.",
    "For each combination of model m and prompt p, we calculate the accuracy of the labels V m,p r for the ground-truth label V r.",
